<P>To the RIGHT HONOURABLE <HI>Sir</HI> THOMAS CHITTY, <HI>Knt.</HI> LORD-MAYOR, THE ALDERMEN, AND CITIZENS of <HI>LONDON,</HI> THIS SERMON, Is, with all RESPECT, Dedicated, by</P>
<CLOSER><SALUTE><HI>Their mo&s;t obliged, and Mo&s;t obedient Servant,</HI></SALUTE>
